<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>OX</title>
        <meta name="description" content="oxQuiz">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
		<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous" />

        <style>
            @font-face { font-family: 'font'; src: url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/projectnoonnu/noonfonts_nine_@1.1/BBTreeGB.woff') format('woff'); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; }
            h6 {
				font-family: 'font', sans-serif;
				font-size: 25px;
			}
            h8 {
				font-family: 'font', sans-serif;
				font-size: 15px;
			}
            div.left {
			  width: 50%;
			  float: left;
			  box-sizing: border-box;
			  background: #ffffff;
			}
			div.right {
			  width: 50%;
			  float: right;
			  box-sizing: border-box;
			  background: #ffffff;
			}
            </style>
    </head>

	<body>

        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" onClick='window.close()' style="float: right;">닫기</button>

        </br>

        <h6 style = "text-align:center;"><b>인류세와 관련된 여러 문제를 해결하라!</b></h6>

        </br>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="left">
                </br>
                <h7><I>아래 문제를 잘 읽고 본인의 생각을 자유롭게 써 주세요!</I></h7>

                <br></br>

                <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="Basic mixed styles example">
                    <table class="table">
                        <tbody>
                        <% for (var i = 0; i < posts.length; i++){ %>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="row"><%= i+1 %></th>
                            <td><h8><b><%= posts[i].sQuestion %></b></h8></td>
                        </tr>
                        <% } %>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="right">
                </br>
                <form action="/short" method="post">
                    <div class="input-group input-group-sm mb-3">
                        <p><I>문제 순서에 맞게 본인의 생각을 자유롭게 서술해 주세요!</I></p>
                        <table class="table">
                            <tbody>
                            <% for (var i = 0; i < posts.length; i++){ %>
                              <tr>
                                <td>
                                    <span class="input-group-text" id="inputGroup-sizing-sm">Answer <%=i+1%></span>
                                    <input type="text" name="ans" class="form-control" aria-label="Sizing example input" aria-describedby="inputGroup-sizing-sm">
                                </td>
                              </tr>
                              <% } %>
                            </tbody>
                          </table>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark" style="float: right;">제출</button>
                </form>

                <img src="1.gif" class="d-block w-100" alt="gif" />

            </div>

	</body>
</html>